<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.8.9">
<l>pēcu mintiru nāma meṭṭeḻut tumcol liniṉṟu piṉṉarum</l>
<l>pēcu vārttammai yuyya vāṅki<supplied>p</supplied>pi  ṟappa ṟukkumpi rāṉiṭam</l>
<l>vāca māmalar nāṟu vārpoḻil cūḻta rumula kukkellām</l>
<l>tēca māyttika ḻumma laitiru vēṅka ṭamaṭai neñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My heart, take refuge at Tiruvēṅkaṭam, the mountain,</l>
<l rend="indent">which shines as a beacon for all the world</l>
<l>Naturally surrounded by broad forests, fragrant from many scented flowers,</l>
<l>The place of the lord who ends [re]birth, receiving to be saved</l>
<l>Those who speak [even] after having incessantly spoken the eight letters</l>
<l rend="indent">of his sweet names which [everyone] speaks.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
